article_title: In ACA's Fifth Year, Doctors Warm To Obamacare

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Even as the Supreme Court weighs a challenge that could pull health insurance from millions of their patients, doctors are warming to life under the Affordable Care Act after five years, a new analysis indicates.
